# Daheim - Home Automation Dashboard

## Project Overview
iOS 26 "Liquid Glass" inspired home automation dashboard built with React + Vite.

**Live URL:** https://thorsten.vercel.app/
**GitHub:** https://github.com/murtopia/thorsten

## Tech Stack
- React 18 + Vite
- Pure CSS (glassmorphism with backdrop-filter)
- Vercel (auto-deploys from GitHub)

